<br>
Five best weapons:<br>
1. Samurai edge gun from Resident Evil. I'm not sure if thats the name. But just watching three bullets rip through a zombie head at close succession is all too rewarding. <br>
<br>
2. Missile launcher from Resident Evil. Hard to get, hard to control, all too good. Unfortunately, there is no such thing as a rocket jump in RE.<br>
<br>
3. Grenade launcher with unlimited ammo. The best. kinda gets boring after a while.<br>
<br>
4. Super Scope from Super Smash Melee. Especially when you can get a rebound off of a pipe or ship plating, The charge up is nearly impossible to dodge, unless you're a pro at the air dodge.<br>
<br>
